---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Contact — Agents of Chaos"
  description="Get in touch with Agents of Chaos about red-teaming engagements, or about joining the team."
>
  <div class="reading">
    <div class="page-head">
      <h1>Contact</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Engagements, collaborations, and hiring.</p>
    </div>

    <p>
      We take on a small number of red-teaming engagements at a time. If you're
      deploying multi-agent systems and want them stress-tested before they reach
      production, write to us.
    </p>

    <p>
      <span class="fb-contact-label">email:</span>
      <a href="mailto:contact@agents-of-chaos.ai">contact@agents-of-chaos.ai</a>
    </p>

    <span class="section-label"><span class="num">·</span>/ joining</span>
    <h2>Working with us</h2>

    <p>
      We occasionally bring on researchers, red-teamers, and engineers for
      campaigns. If red-teaming agentic systems is your kind of problem, reach out
      with a note on what you've built or broken.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
